The query based sampling utility included here is a pre-release of a utility
that will be included in the Lemur toolkit v1.9.  Please see 
http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~lemur for more information about Lemur.

See the file LICENSE in this same directory for the terms of
redistribution and use.


To install the query based sampling utility, first download and install
the Lemur toolkit.  Extract this archive within the lemur base directory.
In the Makefile, add distrib_util to LIBDIRS and distrib_app to APPDIRS.
